{"tid":2400644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"資深泛民提醒大眾千萬不要辱罵法官、檢控官或律師 亦呼籲黎智英要有耐性","createTime":"2021-02-09T06:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T06:04:35.000Z","uid":30788,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3803463de5e8a867e27fddb8f4cd02b5ea5dd464","tid":2400644,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"余若薇續稱，在2020年，被捕者會逐漸上到法庭，大眾需要有無比的耐性，因為必定有很多案件的結果會令大眾嘩然、令大眾不高興，但她提醒，大眾千萬不要辱罵法官、檢控官或律師，甚至燒法院等地方，否則只會被視為野蠻人。她強調，公眾如果認為審訊結果不對，可以作出批評，只要不是人身攻擊或謾罵便可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/26162/%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87-%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB-26171/%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%88%96%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA%EF%BC%8C%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E6%9C%89%E7%AF%80%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%98%AF%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F26162%2F%25E4%25BD%2599%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2596%2587-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB-26171%2F%25E4%25BD%2599%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2596%2587%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25AF%2580%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259A%2584&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=48982cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/26162/%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87-%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB-26171/%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%